#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: weal-profile.php includes/class-weal-profile.php:204
#: includes/class-weal-profile.php:205
msgid "Weal Profile"
msgstr "Weal Profile"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: weal-profile.php
msgid "https://weal.cloud"
msgstr "https://weal.cloud"

#. Description of the plugin
#: weal-profile.php
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Creates a personal account page where logged-in users can manage their "
"profile information, review their site activity, see comment reactions, and "
"earn achievements based on community participation. Client-side caching for "
"improved performance."
msgstr ""
"Crea una página de cuenta personal donde los usuarios registrados pueden "
"gestionar su perfil y revisar su actividad en el sitio."

#. Author of the plugin
